    <item>
      <title>波兰公用事业公司跳水，煤炭分拆被削减，有利于合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/polish-utilities-dive-as-coal-spinoff-axed-in-favor-of-tie-ups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一名高级政府官员概述了放弃煤炭资产分拆、转而将煤矿与发电机连接起来的计划后，波兰电力公司的股价创下 18 个月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/polish-utilities-dive-as-coal-spinoff-axed-in-favor-of-tie-ups</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:53:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盈利乐观情绪支撑中国人工智能推动的新兴市场股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对人工智能和中国刺激措施推动的强劲财报季持乐观态度，新兴市场股市有望创下一个月来最长的连涨纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:43:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的全电动汽车销量在第一季度大幅增长，表现优于特斯拉和大众等竞争对手，后者一直在努力应对疲软的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行维持利率不变，与政府的分歧加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行周三维持利率不变，突显货币政策在支持经济增长方面的局限性，尤其是在财政环境宽松的情况下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/thai-central-bank-holds-rate-deepening-rift-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
