    <item>
      <title>由于债务稳步上升，惠誉将中国前景下调至负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将中国的前景从稳定修正为负面，称政府可能会增加债务，以摆脱房地产驱动的经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/fitch-cuts-china-outlook-to-negative-on-steady-rise-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七与I将把7-11从原来的伊藤洋华堂店中剥离出来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七与i Holdings Co. 正在考虑将伊藤洋华堂（该公司历史悠久的超市零售核心）上市，并最终将其从利润更高、增长更快的 7-11 特许经营权中剥离出来，集中精力将便利店打造成全球业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/seven-i-climbs-on-reports-it-will-sell-ito-yokado-stores-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
